able26歲。她於大約1421年與Sir John Melton 7th Lord Lucy在英國英格蘭德比夏爾結婚。他們至少是1個兒子和2個女兒的父母。她去世於1455年在她的家鄉享年53歲。"},"zh-hans":{"1402–1455":"1402年–1455年","1396–1453":"1396年–1453年","–1453":"–1453年","1398–1455":"1398年–1455年","1422–1500":"1422年–1500年","1425–1458":"1425年–1458年","–1444":"–1444年","1364–1431":"1364年–1431年","1377–1432":"1377年–1432年","1396":"1396年","1425":"1425年","1458":"1458年","1402":"1402年","22 December 1431":"1431年12月22日","1500":"1500年","1422":"1422年","1444":"1444年","1455":"1455年","1432":"1432年","1377":"1377年","1431":"1431年","1398":"1398年","1453":"1453年","1364":"1364年","about 1421":"大约1421年","8 August 1432":"1432年8月8日","Durham, England":"英国達勒姆","Derbyshire, England":"英国英格兰德比夏爾","England":"英国英格兰","Melton Hall, Derbyshire, England":"英国德比夏爾","Holme Pierrepont,,Nottinghamshire,England":"英国英格兰諾廷加姆爾霍爾梅 皮朋特","lifeSummary":"当Elizabeth Hilton于1402年出生在英国德比夏爾时，她的父亲Sir Robert Hilton Knt. Baron of Hilton39岁，母亲Joan Constable26岁。她于大约1421年与Sir John Melton 7th Lord Lucy在英国英格兰德比夏爾结婚。他们至少是1个儿子和2个女儿的父母。她去世于1455年在她的家乡享年53岁。"},"hr":{"1402–1455":"1402.–1455.","1396–1453":"1396–1453","–1453":"–1453","1398–1455":"1398–1455.","1422–1500":"1422.–1500","1425–1458":"1425.–1458","–1444":"–1444.","1364–1431":"1364–1431","1377–1432":"1377–1432","1396":"1396","1425":"1425.","1458":"1458","1402":"1402.","22 December 1431":"22. prosinca 1431.","1500":"1500","1422":"1422.","1444":"1444.","1455":"1455.","1432":"1432","1377":"1377","1431":"1431","1398":"1398","1453":"1453","1364":"1364","about 1421":"oko 1421.","8 August 1432":"8. kolovoza 1432.","Durham, England":"Durham, England","Derbyshire, England":"Derbyshire, Engleska, United Kingdom","England":"Engleska, United Kingdom","Melton Hall, Derbyshire, England":"Derbyshire, England","Holme Pierrepont,,Nottinghamshire,England":"Holme Pierrepont, Nottinghamshire, Engleska, United Kingdom"},"cs":{"1402–1455":"1402–1455","1396–1453":"1396–1453","–1453":"–1453","1398–1455":"1398–1455","1422–1500":"1422–1500","1425–1458":"1425–1458","–1444":"–1444","1364–1431":"1